    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast:Run is a fast-paced racing game that challenges your reflexes and speed. Your goal is to complete levels as quickly as possible without failing </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a variety of levels, each with its own unique set of challenges. You'll need to jump, and dodge to make your way through each level. The faster you complete a level, the higher your score. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast:Run also includes a leaderboard system, allowing you to compete with other players around the world. Can you outrun them all and claim the top spot? With its simple controls and addictive gameplay, Fast:Run is a game that will keep you on the edge of your seat. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Practice (Train on a specific level) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Racing (Get the best time by covering all the maps, alone or against other players) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Infinite (Run on a randomly generated infinite map) </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ghost of the best times (Understand how the best players play)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wall Jump </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Boost In Air </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Jump Pad </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Zipline </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Various powerups</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Updates planned:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Add a level editor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Workshop (mod.io)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross Platform</p></li></ul>",
